MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 2109

AMENDING PROCLAMATION NO. 367 DATED MAY 2, 1994 WHICH RESERVED A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND IN STA. ANA DISTRICT, DAVAO CITY AS OFFICE SITE FOR THE DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENT AND NATURAL RESOURCES, REGION XI, BY SEGREGATING A PORTION THEREOF AND RESERVING THE SAME AS OFFICE SITE FOR THE OFFICE OF THE OMBUDSMAN-MINDANAO

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby segregate a portion of the land covered by Proclamation No. 367, s. 1994 for the DENR Regional Office Building, located in Sta. Ana District, City of Davao, containing an area of 2,085 square meters, and reserve ONE THOUSAND SQUARE METERS of its as the site for the OMB-Mindanao office building, more particularly described as follows:

“LOT 5012-K-7-A (New) PROPOSED OMB-Mindanao Office Site

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 5012, K-7-(*New), A portion of Lot 5012, K-7, Plan SWO-11-000506) situated in Sta. Ana District, City of Davao, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the West, along lines 1-2-3 by De Guzman St.; On the North, along line 3-4 by 4th Avenue; On the East, along lines 4-5-6 by Fernandez St.; On the South, along line 6-1 by Lot 5012, K-7-B(New). Beginning at a point marked 1, Being N. 51 deg. 57 min. E., 6351.12 m. from BLLM No. 22, Cad 102, Davao Cadastre;

17.82 m. to point 2;

04.52 m. to point 3;

41.99 m. to point 4;

04.43 m. to point 5;

17.50 m. to point 6;

47.73 m. to point of beginning

Containing an area of ONE THOUSAND (1000) SQ. METERS more or less.

LOT 5012, K-7-B(NEW) PROPOSED DENR XI REGIONAL OFFICE SITE

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 5012, K-7-B(New), a portion of Lot 5012, K-7 of Plan Swo-11-000506) situated in Sta. Ana District, City of Davao, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the West, along line 6-1 by De Guzman St.; On the North, K-7-A(New); On the East, along line 2-3 by Fernandez St.; On the South, along lines 3-4-5 by 3rd Avenue. Beginning at appoint marked 1, Being N. 51 deg., 57 min. E., 6351.12 m. from BLLM No. 22, Cad 102, Davao Cadastre;

47.73 m. to point 2;

19.29 m. to point 3;

04.61 m. to point 4;

42.62 m. to point 5;

03.19 m. to point 6;

20.88 m. to point beginning

Containing an area of ONE THOUSAND EIGHTY FIVE (1085) SQUARE METERS , more or less.”

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 29th day of June , in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Ten.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) LEANDRO R. MENDOZA Executive Secretary

